extendedInfo.description: Print directly from your phone or tablet via WiFi, Bluetooth or USB cable without a computer.Note: PrintHand app is NOT FREE. We recommend printing test page prior to upgrade.You can print:- Office documents (DOC, XLS, PPT, PDF, TXT)- Images and photos- Emails and attachments- Web pages- Calendar, call log, text messages- Facebook albums- Files from Google Drive, Dropbox, Box, SugarSync- Content from business apps such as OfficeSuite, DocumentsToGo, QuickOffice, Exchange, EverNote and more via Share option The app is similar to (and better than!) popular PrinterShare.Printing to Mac or Windows shared printers, Workgroup, Domain and Active Directory and Google Cloud.
